description:
This is a 21 minute workout called '20 min Full Body STRETCH/YOGA for STRESS & ANXIETY Relief' from the channel MadFit.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: De-stress with this 20 minute calming yoga routine that includes light and easy full body stretches for stress relief and anxiety.
